trans-unit.source: Enumeration of activity result values that qualifies the state of an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> that has an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus" /> of <see langword="Closed" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" />의 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus" />가 있는 <see langword="Closed" />의 상태를 한정하는 활동 결과 값의 열거입니다.

trans-unit.source: Result represents the final status of an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> instance within a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 결과는 워크플로 인스턴스 내 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> 인스턴스의 최종 상태를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The values of the enumeration are based upon the activity state diagram that is determined by the activity-engine contract.
trans-unit.target: 열거의 값은 활동 엔진 계약에 의해 결정되는 활동 상태 다이어그램을 기반으로 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Values other than None are allowed only for an activity whose <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> is <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>.
trans-unit.target: "없음" 이외의 값은 활동에 대해서만 인 허용 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> 은 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the canceling state.
trans-unit.target: 활동이 Canceling 상태에서 Closed 상태로 전환되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the compensating state.
trans-unit.target: 활동이 Compensating 상태에서 Closed 상태로 전환되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the faulting state.
trans-unit.target: 활동이 Faulting 상태에서 Closed 상태로 전환되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: The activity is not in the <see cref="F:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed" /> state.
The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the executing state.
trans-unit.target: 활동이 Executing 상태에서 Closed 상태로 전환되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the initialized state.
trans-unit.target: 활동이 Initialized 상태에서 Closed 상태로 전환되었습니다.
